  "texts": [
    "(2) Limited integration of fake review detection and preference analysis.",
    "Most existing studies treat fake review detection and user preference analysis as independent tasks.",
    "However, integrating these two tasks could improve the reliability of insights derived from user feedback by ensuring that preference analysis is based on authentic reviews.",
    "This integration remains unexplored in the current literature.",
    "(3) Insufficient consideration of the hidden design features."
  ]
}